Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.40,0:24:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是本周的宇宙照片
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.36,0:24:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.52,0:24:10.03,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本周的宇宙照片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.21,0:00:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选拔宇航员的第三次测试
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.80,0:00:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封闭舱之中的两周生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的课题是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从同伴之中自己选出两名最适合当宇航员的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.35,0:00:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福田先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和靖先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新田
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和芹夏小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.07,0:00:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后还有我..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意让我们自己选
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.78,0:00:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是想看我们是否具备舍弃别人的冷酷决心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.41,0:00:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.14,0:00:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用哪一个比较开心来决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用猜拳来决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有像拳头一样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.82,0:00:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有像剪刀一样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.98,0:00:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有像布一样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底谁是最强的..有人知道答案吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.13,0:00:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像他的风格呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:00:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可话说回来 我并不是觉得猜拳本身很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.25,0:01:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.69,0:01:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在这愉快的两周时光结束的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们五个人都能开开心心地走出来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.84,0:01:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这只是我一厢情愿的想法..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我的想法传达给了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.48,0:01:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样终于能结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:01:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.94,0:02:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头剪子..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.94,0:02:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.00,0:02:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜负只用一次就决出了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人赢了 三个人输了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.75,0:02:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人觉得胜者似乎一开始就注定了是这两人..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世上也有这样的猜拳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 请出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.31,0:05:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.17,0:05:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 完全给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来还有这么个玩意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附时钟的巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回程也要搭这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿六
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 看起来很精神嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着一副精神奕奕的表情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 各位~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.91,0:06:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不想看一看久违的天空啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这边来吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 这里不是什么机密设施吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以到外面去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那个..已经没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:06:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开门！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耀眼~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是真正的天空好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.44,0:07:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.88,0:07:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是JAXA吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是巴士的出发点啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都被JAXA给骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很失望吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:07:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很失望吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:07:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很失望对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？瞧你那副不得要领的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜中了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜..猜中了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.74,0:08:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗憾的是我们没有建立机密设施的资金
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那辆铁皮补丁车是我们的技术人员改造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是造那个就已经够呛了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.96,0:08:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个各位 请大家移动至E-2栋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:08:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 贤治..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是三次测试里的东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个 白色的拼图
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.47,0:09:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:17.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}北村绘名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:17.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}这两周虽然发生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:17.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}但是非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:17.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}有真壁先生在真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:17.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}今后也请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:17.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}手岛有利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:17.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}谢谢！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:17.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}沟口大和
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:17.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}恭喜你完成拼图
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:17.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}富井龙之介
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:17.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}有机会再一起聊一聊宇宙的神秘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成的时候 JAXA的工作人员说我可以留着它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是作为纪念 我就让B班的各位在上面签了名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.86,0:09:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞的好像集体签名图一样..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是青春男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是汤汤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 谢谢你谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.64,0:09:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么汤呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶..橡栗..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 南波先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请喝咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到家之后他马上就摆出来了呢 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个看起来很专业的签名是谁的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.68,0:09:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沟口？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他的心目中 成为宇航员是板上钉钉的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是赢不了他那拼命劲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他按照自己的计划继续前行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我则没能留下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.91,0:10:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊 贤治
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理事长不是说了最后还有机会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了各位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同各位猜测的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.19,0:10:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个班选出的那两人并不是马上就会成为宇航员
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.33,0:10:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次选出的共计六人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将和我们所挑选出的数人一起前往休斯顿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休斯顿？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而最后将在休斯顿的NASA参加一场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.14,0:10:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由现役宇航员把关的一日面试
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这次没被选上的各位说不定也还有机会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而就算选上了也还要过休斯顿那一关
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然也把希望寄托在那个机会上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:10:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只能指望那个机会了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橡栗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你就是古谷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于来了呢 辛苦了辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马..马场先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初..初次见面！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是古谷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有点离太远了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.32,0:11:56.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.32,0:11:56.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}我的名字叫古谷靖志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.32,0:11:56.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}不好意思我等不及要先说一句
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.32,0:11:56.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}这次您的开发让我这种无可奈何必须选择放弃的人又看到了希望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 你也是关西人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.98,0:12:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我是京都人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.59,0:12:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 我是大阪人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算身在筑波 胸膛里还是一颗大阪心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.47,0:12:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人也真的好小
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.31,0:12:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我差不多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也一直和你抱有一样的自卑情绪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一开始就不得不放弃成为宇航员的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从你第一次给我发邮件已经过去了三年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.89,0:12:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是时光飞逝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.28,0:12:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你随便坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实啊 除了你之外各地也传来很多振奋的邮件和传真
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.89,0:12:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都对我开发出这套宇航服表示感激和感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:12:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你的信是最令人热血沸腾的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这..这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上田 麻烦拿两杯卡尔必思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.27,0:13:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要加牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古谷是不是要掺水的呢 卡尔必思？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 也帮我加牛奶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是老妈的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们两个都是喝同样的东西长大的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.81,0:13:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算知道已经长不高了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是会习惯性地喝下去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没想到那个传邮件的青年真的能突破到第三次测试
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是很不得了的事情啊 古谷！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马场先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在邮件中实在是夸下了海口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:49.76,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会成为宇航员的 您看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:13:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最后的最后..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在猜拳中输掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？猜拳？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.99,0:14:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是牛奶卡尔必思七兑三
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.87,0:14:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊..谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 古谷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.79,0:14:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看一下实物啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的宇宙服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我超想看的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.44,0:14:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 绿色的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.59,0:15:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绿..？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人 等一下是要去约会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.82,0:15:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 看上去不像有女朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拧我拧..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 贤治
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:15:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南波先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.12,0:16:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对..对不起 我来迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.60,0:16:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芹夏小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.81,0:16:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 真的十分对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀唔~真是高兴死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能和芹夏小姐在外面共进晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我一点不..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.64,0:16:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古谷也还没有来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 古谷发来邮件了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说会迟到15分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.64,0:16:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.04,0:16:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就在里面等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这帮人也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.07,0:16:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了你的眼睛 干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.51,0:16:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是两人独处的话该有多好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:16:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是关于宇宙的书哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看啊 宇宙非常地广袤而美丽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想去宇宙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.02,0:17:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我十三岁的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.31,0:17:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近的文具店搞抽奖的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.38,0:17:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得到了五等奖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是宇航员的垫板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正面是宇航员的照片
